I've been seeing Stephen for my haircuts and salon services for about eight years now, which is officially longer than any relationship I've ever had. It was exciting news to find out that he'd ventured out to open his own space, which is tucked inside the Moda Fina Studios on Camelback. There's nothing worse than finding out your hair stylist has moved to a new salon, so the side benefit of this opening, is that I'll always know where to find him.   The salon features exclusive Kevin Murphy hair products, a comfortable, chic space and the best hair guy in town. Love it.

